    "description": "<strong>Description:</strong><br>Dive into the relentless action of Defender, a thrilling roguelike wave-based game where your survival depends on your skill and strategy. Face off against hordes of basic monsters, formidable elites, and fearsome bosses. Navigate the battlefield with WASD controls, and unleash your attacks with precision using your mouse. Each wave completed grants you the chance to level up, enhancing your character's abilities and preparing you for even more challenging foes. Will you rise to the top and become the ultimate monster slayer?<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Intense wave-based combat<br></li><li>Variety of enemies including basic monsters, elites, and bosses<br></li><li>WASD movement and mouse-based attacks<br></li><li>Progressive leveling system<br></li><li>Dynamic and engaging gameplay</li></ul>",
